These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, mouse, cat
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the cat##7
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | mouse | turtle | cat | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, cabbage, corn, cauliflower
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating corn is somewhere between the person eating cabbage and the person eating raspberry##7
3. the person eating corn is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating cauliflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | raspberry | cauliflower | corn | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
