1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person eating corn is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating tomato##7
3. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | spinach | tomato | corn | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, van, roller
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the taxi##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | van | motorbike | roller | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, time-travel, sports, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
4. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama | time-travel | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indian, brazilian, indonesian
1. the italian is somewhere between the indonesian and the indian##7
2. the brazilian is somewhere between the italian and the indonesian##7
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
4. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | brazilian | italian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, sprite, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking coffee##7
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking water##7
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade | sprite | water |

