2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person watching musical movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | scientific | musical |

