2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the roller##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | roller | boat | motorbike | skateboard |

